{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a reusable Shopify Online Store 2.0 section called "Feature Row" to be placed directly below the introductory paragraph on the About Us page.
    
    OBJECTIVE
    Build a clean, premium, minimal feature row that highlights the brand's core principles. The design should feel elegant and lightweight, with no visual clutter.
    
    LAYOUT
    - Display 3 feature items in a single horizontal row on desktop.
    - On tablet, maintain three columns if space permits; otherwise wrap gracefully.
    - On mobile, stack vertically or use a responsive 2+1 layout depending on available width.
    - Center-align all content.
    - Use generous whitespace.
    - Do NOT use cards.
    - Do NOT use borders.
    - Do NOT use shadows.
    - Do NOT use colored boxes or containers.
    - Keep the design extremely minimal.
    
    DEFAULT CONTENT
    
    Feature 1
    Icon:
    🌿
    Title:
    Ayurvedic Inspired
    
    Feature 2
    Icon:
    ⚗️
    Title:
    Science Backed
    
    Feature 3
    Icon:
    ❤️
    Title:
    Made for Long-Term Wellness
    
    Each feature should contain only:
    - Icon
    - Title
    
    No descriptions.
    
    TYPOGRAPHY
    - Icon should be visually prominent.
    - Title should use the theme typography.
    - Keep typography clean and premium.
    - Maintain consistent spacing between icon and title.
    
    SECTION SETTINGS (Editable)
    Nothing should be hardcoded.
    
    Include editable controls for:
    - Section heading (optional)
    - Background color
    - Content width (Full / Standard / Narrow)
    - Top padding
    - Bottom padding
    - Horizontal alignment
    - Gap between feature items
    - Gap between icon and title
    - Icon size
    - Title font size
    - Title font weight
    - Maximum content width
    
    FEATURE BLOCK SETTINGS
    Each feature should be created as a repeatable block so merchants can add, remove, reorder, or duplicate features.
    
    Each block should include:
    - Icon Type selector
        - Emoji
        - SVG
        - Image
    - Emoji field
    - SVG code field
    - Image picker
    - Title text
    - Icon color
    - Title color
    - Optional link
    - Enable/Disable toggle
    
    RESPONSIVE REQUIREMENTS
    Desktop:
    - Three equal-width columns.
    
    Tablet:
    - Responsive wrapping without breaking alignment.
    
    Mobile:
    - Stack vertically or use an optimized 2+1 layout.
    - Icons remain centered.
    - Text remains centered.
    - Prevent overflow.
    - Maintain comfortable spacing.
    
    ACCESSIBILITY
    - Use semantic HTML.
    - Decorative icons should be hidden from screen readers unless an accessible label is provided.
    - Maintain WCAG-compliant color contrast.
    - Ensure keyboard accessibility if links are enabled.
    
    PERFORMANCE
    - Build as a native Shopify Online Store 2.0 section.
    - Use Section + Blocks architecture.
    - No hardcoded content.
    - No unnecessary JavaScript.
    - Use CSS Grid or Flexbox for responsiveness.
    - Follow Shopify theme best practices.
    - Optimize for fast loading.
    
    DESIGN DIRECTION
    The section should communicate trust in a refined and understated way. It should seamlessly blend into a premium wellness brand aesthetic, emphasizing simplicity, balance, and elegance rather than decorative styling.
{% enddoc %}
{% liquid
  assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase
%}

{% style %}
  .ai-feature-row-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    padding-top: {{ block.settings.padding_top }}px;
    padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.padding_bottom }}px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .ai-feature-row-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
    {% if block.settings.content_width == 'full' %}
      max-width: 100%;
    {% elsif block.settings.content_width == 'narrow' %}
      max-width: calc({{ block.settings.max_content_width }}px * 0.75);
    {% else %}
      max-width: {{ block.settings.max_content_width }}px;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-feature-row-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: {{ block.settings.horizontal_alignment }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.heading_bottom_spacing }}px 0;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
  }

  .ai-feature-row-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: {{ block.settings.gap_between_items }}px;
    text-align: {{ block.settings.horizontal_alignment }};
  }

  .ai-feature-row-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: {% if block.settings.horizontal_alignment == 'left' %}flex-start{% elsif block.settings.horizontal_alignment == 'right' %}flex-end{% else %}center{% endif %};
    gap: {{ block.settings.gap_icon_title }}px;
  }

  .ai-feature-row-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: {{ block.settings.icon_color_1 }};
  }

  .ai-feature-row-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    fill: currentColor;
  }

  .ai-feature-row-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} img {
    width: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .ai-feature-row-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.title_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.title_font_weight }};
    color: {{ block.settings.title_color_1 }};
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .ai-feature-row-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(2) .ai-feature-row-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.icon_color_2 }};
  }

  .ai-feature-row-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(2) .ai-feature-row-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.title_color_2 }};
  }

  .ai-feature-row-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(3) .ai-feature-row-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.icon_color_3 }};
  }

  .ai-feature-row-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(3) .ai-feature-row-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.title_color_3 }};
  }

  .ai-feature-row-link-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: {% if block.settings.horizontal_alignment == 'left' %}flex-start{% elsif block.settings.horizontal_alignment == 'right' %}flex-end{% else %}center{% endif %};
    gap: {{ block.settings.gap_icon_title }}px;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .ai-feature-row-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .ai-feature-row-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}:last-child:nth-child(odd) {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      max-width: 50%;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-feature-row-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding-top: {{ block.settings.padding_top | times: 0.7 | round }}px;
      padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.padding_bottom | times: 0.7 | round }}px;
    }

    .ai-feature-row-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: {{ block.settings.gap_between_items | times: 0.8 | round }}px;
    }

    .ai-feature-row-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}:last-child:nth-child(odd) {
      grid-column: auto;
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .ai-feature-row-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.icon_size | times: 0.9 | round }}px;
    }

    .ai-feature-row-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
      width: {{ block.settings.icon_size | times: 0.9 | round }}px;
      height: {{ block.settings.icon_size | times: 0.9 | round }}px;
    }

    .ai-feature-row-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} img {
      width: {{ block.settings.icon_size | times: 0.9 | round }}px;
      height: {{ block.settings.icon_size | times: 0.9 | round }}px;
    }

    .ai-feature-row-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.title_font_size | times: 0.9 | round }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="ai-feature-row-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-feature-row-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% if block.settings.heading != blank %}
      <h2 class="ai-feature-row-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h2>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="ai-feature-row-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.feature_1_enabled %}
        <div class="ai-feature-row-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if block.settings.feature_1_link != blank %}
            <a href="{{ block.settings.feature_1_link }}" class="ai-feature-row-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-label="{{ block.settings.feature_1_title | escape }}">
          {% endif %}

          <div class="ai-feature-row-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-hidden="true">
            {% if block.settings.feature_1_icon_type == 'emoji' and block.settings.feature_1_emoji != blank %}
              {{ block.settings.feature_1_emoji }}
            {% elsif block.settings.feature_1_icon_type == 'svg' and block.settings.feature_1_svg_code != blank %}
              {{ block.settings.feature_1_svg_code }}
            {% elsif block.settings.feature_1_icon_type == 'image' and block.settings.feature_1_icon_image != blank %}
              <img 
                src="{{ block.settings.feature_1_icon_image | image_url: width: 200 }}" 
                alt=""
                loading="lazy"
                width="{{ block.settings.icon_size }}"
                height="{{ block.settings.icon_size }}"
              >
            {% endif %}
          </div>

          {% if block.settings.feature_1_title != blank %}
            <h3 class="ai-feature-row-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.feature_1_title }}</h3>
          {% endif %}

          {% if block.settings.feature_1_link != blank %}
            </a>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.feature_2_enabled %}
        <div class="ai-feature-row-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if block.settings.feature_2_link != blank %}
            <a href="{{ block.settings.feature_2_link }}" class="ai-feature-row-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-label="{{ block.settings.feature_2_title | escape }}">
          {% endif %}

          <div class="ai-feature-row-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-hidden="true">
            {% if block.settings.feature_2_icon_type == 'emoji' and block.settings.feature_2_emoji != blank %}
              {{ block.settings.feature_2_emoji }}
            {% elsif block.settings.feature_2_icon_type == 'svg' and block.settings.feature_2_svg_code != blank %}
              {{ block.settings.feature_2_svg_code }}
            {% elsif block.settings.feature_2_icon_type == 'image' and block.settings.feature_2_icon_image != blank %}
              <img 
                src="{{ block.settings.feature_2_icon_image | image_url: width: 200 }}" 
                alt=""
                loading="lazy"
                width="{{ block.settings.icon_size }}"
                height="{{ block.settings.icon_size }}"
              >
            {% endif %}
          </div>

          {% if block.settings.feature_2_title != blank %}
            <h3 class="ai-feature-row-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.feature_2_title }}</h3>
          {% endif %}

          {% if block.settings.feature_2_link != blank %}
            </a>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.feature_3_enabled %}
        <div class="ai-feature-row-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if block.settings.feature_3_link != blank %}
            <a href="{{ block.settings.feature_3_link }}" class="ai-feature-row-link-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-label="{{ block.settings.feature_3_title | escape }}">
          {% endif %}

          <div class="ai-feature-row-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" aria-hidden="true">
            {% if block.settings.feature_3_icon_type == 'emoji' and block.settings.feature_3_emoji != blank %}
              {{ block.settings.feature_3_emoji }}
            {% elsif block.settings.feature_3_icon_type == 'svg' and block.settings.feature_3_svg_code != blank %}
              {{ block.settings.feature_3_svg_code }}
            {% elsif block.settings.feature_3_icon_type == 'image' and block.settings.feature_3_icon_image != blank %}
              <img 
                src="{{ block.settings.feature_3_icon_image | image_url: width: 200 }}" 
                alt=""
                loading="lazy"
                width="{{ block.settings.icon_size }}"
                height="{{ block.settings.icon_size }}"
              >
            {% endif %}
          </div>

          {% if block.settings.feature_3_title != blank %}
            <h3 class="ai-feature-row-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.feature_3_title }}</h3>
          {% endif %}

          {% if block.settings.feature_3_link != blank %}
            </a>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

